" Multiple cursors.
nnoremap <C-n> gh
snoremap <C-n> j
snoremap <C-p> k
snoremap <C-x> l
snoremap i <Esc>i

" Duece Seven.
nnoremap zc :Fold<CR>
nnoremap zM :FoldAll<CR>
nnoremap zo :Unfold<CR>
nnoremap zR :UnfoldAll<CR>

" " Prestige.
" nnoremap <leader>r :RevealInSideBar<CR>

" " Roger.
" nnoremap <C-c> :Copy<CR>

" " Files.
" nnoremap <leader>h :HidePhantoms<CR>
" nnoremap <leader>sf :ShowFindInFiles<CR>
" nnoremap <leader>sr :ShowFindResults<CR>

" Sorting.
" TODO Add `:sort u` Neovintageous ex command.
vnoremap <leader>sl <F9>o<Esc>
nnoremap <leader>ss vip<F9>o<Esc>

" It's a Bird... It's a Plane...
nnoremap <D-n> :TestNearest<CR>
nnoremap <D-i> :GotoSymbolInProject<CR>

" AceJump plugin
" https://packagecontrol.io/packages/AceJump
nnoremap <leader><leader>a :AceJumpAfter<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>c :AceJumpChar<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>d :AceJumpAddCursor<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>i :AceJumpWithinLine<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>l :AceJumpLine<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>s :AceJumpSelect<CR>
nnoremap <leader><leader>w :AceJumpWord<CR>

" ColorSchemeUnit plugin
" https://github.com/gerardroche/sublime-color-scheme-unit
nnoremap <leader>ia :ColorSchemeUnitInsertAssertions<CR>
nnoremap <leader>is :ColorSchemeUnitInsertSyntaxAssertions<CR>

" Gimmie Shelter.
nnoremap <leader>gi :FormatGithubUrl<CR>
nnoremap <leader>go :GitOpen<CR>
nnoremap <leader>gt :TaskList<CR>

" Fuck it.
nnoremap <leader>vd :VarDump<CR>

nnoremap <leader><leader>f :FocusUnitTestingPanel<CR>
